          "description": "I can\u2019t say enough great things about Stacy. From the moment I walked into the office, she made me feel comfortable, heard, and genuinely cared for. She is incredibly professional, knowledgeable, and patient but what really stands out is her compassion.\n\nDuring a time when I\u2019ve been dealing with health concerns, Stacy took the time to explain everything clearly, answer my questions, and make sure I understood the next steps. She never made me feel rushed, and she always treated me with kindness and respect.\n\nIt\u2019s rare to find someone who balances medical expertise with such a warm bedside manner. She truly goes above and beyond for her patients, and it shows.\n\nThe office is lucky to have her and so are the patients.",
